com.orm.androrm
Class Model

java.lang.Object
  com.orm.androrm.Model

public abstract class Model
extends Object

This is the superclass of all models, that can be stored/ read to/ from the database automatically.

Philipp Giese

getFields

protected static final <T extends Model> List<Field> getFields(Class<T> clazz,
                                                               T instance)
Retrieves all fields of a given class, that are
  1. NOT private
  2. Database fields
In addition these fields are set to be accessible, so that they can then be further processed.

Type Parameters:
T -
Parameters:
clazz - Class to extract the fields from.
instance - Instance of that class.
Returns:
List of all fields, that are database fields, and that are NOT private.
